 border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-styl=
e: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> pretending to be upstarts</a> who were =
disrupting traditional Wall Street=E2=80=99s stranglehold on going public. =
=E2=80=9CInvest with us because we are deeply tied in to the world of capit=
al and big institutions love us=E2=80=9D is a good pitch, but =E2=80=9Cinve=
st with us because we are totally outside of the world of capital and big i=
nstitutions hate us=E2=80=9D is =E2=80=A6=C2=A0also a pitch ... that =E2=80=
