gin: 16px 0;">If you are a successful investor with deep ties to traditiona=
l Wall Street, you can go ahead and do that pitch, it=E2=80=99s a free coun=
try, but if that is the pitch that works then why shouldn=E2=80=99t random =
young people launch their own SPACs? Here are Bloomberg=E2=80=99s <a href=
